Author: ICObox
Title: üåüüí∞[ANN] ICOBox (ICOS): Tokens of promising ICOs, at 75% off + Referral Program
Body: Meet ICOBox team: ICOBox would likely have taken an entirely different shape if it were not for one of our co-founders, Anar Babaev. Anar is an extraordinary person: solid as a rock, he is our voice of reason, the calm amid the storm, someone who can actually soothe and talk sense into a dozen unruly blockchain creatives. He appears in public so rarely that rumors abound that he is not a real person, but a group of clandestine developers operating under a collective handle. However, people who knew him before blockchain insist that Anar used to circulate and was recognized as a marketing guru, author of books and an inspirational speaker. Nowadays he prefers online communication (from his secret bunker, we wonder?) to any in-person meeting or interview. We, his colleagues, suspect that the rumors about Anar's non-existence are most likely being spread by Daria Generalova, who, in the two years of working closely with him, with endless calls and messages, so far has not managed to meet him in person.

The centralized nature of present cloud-based transcoding technology is prohibitively expensive and inadequate, with inevitable delays due to hardware limitations. The Transcodium system averts these problems through its peer-to-peer solution that allows multiple nodes to provide quick deliverability. The platform operates using TNS tokens, which are also rewarded to worker nodes upon successful conversion and delivery. More information at https://icos.icobox.io/projects/1845

Author: ICObox
Title: üåüüí∞[ANN] ICOBox (ICOS): Tokens of promising ICOs, at 75% off + Referral Program
Body: Meet ICOBox team: ICOBox is a fruit of labor of a tight-knit team whose members are spread all over the world. We would like to introduce you to several key team members, and as a start we would like to tell you about our legendary co-founder Nick Evdokimov, without whom ICOBox most likely would not even exist. Nick is an inspiration for the entire team, a determined visionary who never rests on his laurels. His brilliant intellect works nonstop, and he is constantly pushing the boundaries of what's possible with his incredible imagination: Nick has singlehandedly designed over 40 unique tokens and invented three key token models that are widely used today. He's constantly dividing his time not only between numerous projects but also between cities, living between San Francisco and Los Angeles and regularly visiting New York City. Only two questions exist for him: "How to do the impossible?" and "Where can I find the time to do it?" Having worked side by side with Nick for the past year, we are convinced: he is a genius. This is why we normally like to keep mum about him ‚Äì we don't want him to get hijacked.

Body: ICOS platform update: There have been 591,617 ICOS tokens issued to date, and 40,291 of them are in frozen mode. 18,000 ICOS tokens have been destroyed. ICOS program is a way for promising but underfunded projects to receive ICOBox's tools and assistance in conducting their ICOs. Any project is welcome to apply. ICOBox prescreens the applicants but the final selection of candidates for an ICO covered through ICOS program is made by the vote of ICOS token holders. In exchange for the ICOBox's services the new project makes its future tokens available to ICOS token holders. These tokens are to be placed on icos.icobox.io platform, and ICOS token holders can exchange their ICOS tokens for the new tokens. The exchange value per one ICOS token is set at 0.04 BTC, which means that every ICOS token can be exchanged for the relevant number of the new projects' tokens placed on ICOS platform and worth 0.04 BTC at presale prices.

Body: ICOS Swap update: On Tuesday, May 1, the last batch of CannaSOS tokens will be available to ICOS token holders for a swap. CannaSOS is a global blockchain solution for point-of-sale and distribution issues faced by online medical and recreational marijuana dispensaries. Today, many jurisdictions are legalizing cannabis use, but uneven regulatory controls continue to dog the industry. For example, dispensaries‚Äô inability to accept credit card and online banking payments limit transaction transparency. Driven by its PerksCoin (PCT), CannaSOS‚Äôs platform ensures the security of all transactions between dispensaries and buyers. The founders expect that the new service will also help forge strategic partnerships with other mainstream POS-based retailers. More information at https://icos.icobox.io/projects/418

The centralized nature of present cloud-based transcoding technology is prohibitively expensive and inadequate, with inevitable delays due to hardware limitations. The Transcodium system averts these problems through its peer-to-peer solution that allows multiple nodes to provide quick deliverability. The platform operates using TNS tokens, which are also rewarded to worker nodes upon successful conversion and delivery. More information at https://icos.icobox.io/projects/1845

Body: ICOS platform update: There have been 591,617 ICOS tokens issued to date, and 29,141 of them are in frozen mode. 18,000 ICOS tokens have been destroyed. ICOS program is a way for promising but underfunded projects to receive ICOBox's tools and assistance in conducting their ICOs. Any project is welcome to apply. ICOBox prescreens the applicants but the final selection of candidates for an ICO covered through ICOS program is made by the vote of ICOS token holders. In exchange for the ICOBox's services the new project makes its future tokens available to ICOS token holders. These tokens are to be placed on icos.icobox.io platform, and ICOS token holders can exchange their ICOS tokens for the new tokens. The exchange value per one ICOS token is set at 0.04 BTC, which means that every ICOS token can be exchanged for the relevant number of the new projects' tokens placed on ICOS platform and worth 0.04 BTC at presale prices.

Title: üåüüí∞[ANN] ICOBox (ICOS): Tokens of promising ICOs, at 75% off + Referral Program
Body: ICOS Exchange update: PerksCoin (PCT) by CannaSOS will be available for ICOS token exchange on Tuesday, February 6. CannaSOS is the global blockchain solution for point-of-sale and distribution issues faced by online medical and recreational marijuana dispensaries. Today, many jurisdictions are legalizing cannabis use, but uneven regulatory controls continue to dog the industry. For example, dispensaries‚Äô inability to accept credit cards and online banking payments limit transaction transparency. Driven by its PerksCoin, CannaSOS‚Äôs platform ensures the security of all transactions between dispensaries and buyers. The founders expect that the new service will also help forge strategic partnerships with other mainstream POS-based retailers. Learn more: https://icos.icobox.io/projects/418

Title: üåüüí∞[ANN] ICOBox (ICOS): Tokens of promising ICOs, at 75% off + Referral Program
Body: ICOS Exchange update: PARKGENE is a peer-to-peer parking locating and booking service which operates similarly to Airbnb. The project seeks to disrupt a $100 billion largely ‚Äúoffline‚Äù parking industry while simultaneously streamlining parking - thus making the urban environment greener. The platform runs on Ethereum smart contracts and offers an incentivized feedback system. In addition, PARGENE seeks to synergize other elements of the automotive services industry with the GENE token as a tradeable currency. During the ICO, GENE tokens will be available for purchase with fiat or cryptocurrencies. ICOS token holders will be able to swap them on GENE tokens on Tuesday, February 6. https://icos.icobox.io/projects/1123

Author: ICObox
Title: üåüüí∞[ANN] ICOBox (ICOS): Tokens of promising ICOs, at 75% off + Referral Program
Body: ICOBox is glad to announce the launch of the ICOS program! The new projects' tokens will be made available in step with the progress of the relevant ICO: 10% at presale, 10% at the start of public ICO, 30% at the completion of the ICO, 25% one month after the completion of the ICO, and 25% two months after the completion of the ICO. In the first 24 hours since the new token portion has been made available the tokens will be distributed proportionally to the number of received requests. After that, they will be distributed on the first come, first served basis. The exchange value of one ICOS token is 0.04 BTC. Find the first projects participating in the program at https://icos.icobox.io/projects/icos-exchange In several hours tokens of Darenta will be available for exchange on ICOS platform. This is a peer-to-peer car rental marketplace connecting people who need to rent a private car with vehicle owners. Travelers choose from a unique selection of nearby cars, while car owners earn extra money and help fuel the adventures of travelers they meet along the way. The company's PRO tokens power the system and offer their holders multiple benefits and rewards. Learn more at https://icos.icobox.io/projects/560 Native Video Box, one of ICOS projects, which starts offering its tokens for exchange today, is an independent native video platform which shares 80% of revenue from ad views with those who actually create video content and bring it to the audience. By utilizing cutting-edge technologies of programmatic advertising, blockchain and tokenization NVB is changing the way the game is played. NVB tokens serve as a means of payment within the system. Learn more at https://icos.icobox.io/projects/438

Title: üåüüí∞[ANN] ICOBox (ICOS): Tokens of promising ICOs, at 75% off + Referral Program
Body: Within the past 24 hours the Ethereum network experienced, and in the near term may continue to experience technical issues which could delay the delivery of tokens and payments based on the Ethereum platform. Depending on the nature of these issues, the ICOS token may also be affected, as it is built on the Ethereum platform. These network issues are likely the result of an overwhelming amount of transactions on a popular project unrelated to ICOS tokens. We anticipate that no ICOS tokens or related transactions will be lost, but the risk of network delays remains, subject to any actual network issues that may occur.

Author: ICObox
Title: üåüüí∞[ANN] ICOBox (ICOS): Tokens of promising ICOs, at 75% off + Referral Program
Body: We are pleased to announce that the first ever swap on the ICOS platform has been completed! To ensure that the swap process is as transparent and straightforward as possible, we made a few changes: 1) A hold will now be put on ICOS tokens when an ICOS token swap request is submitted (i.e. the same tokens cannot be used for swap more than once). 2) We established a limit for major ICOS token holders, to prevent them from submitting a request that exceeds the total supply of tokens. This will allow all ICOS token holders to take part in the swap on equal terms. In total, the book building for the PRG token swap was oversubscribed by 4.66 times (8.19 times before the introduction of limits), and the rights to future tokens were distributed to the eligible holders. You will be able to withdraw your PRG tokens as soon as they are issued by Paragon after the completion of its ICO and deposited into your account on ICOS platform. Until that time, the swap represents a pledge. For more details on IpTS program, see: https://medium.com/icobox-io/what-is-icobox-interproject-token-swap-ipts-feature-c65629c06df.

Title: üåüüí∞[ANN] ICOBox (ICOS): Tokens of promising ICOs, at 75% off + Referral Program
Body: WARNING to all crypto traders. I would exercise caution in participating in any ICO from CRYPTONOMOS. I purchased WTT tokens via bank transfer but did not receive my tokens. Quote from Cyrptonomos on WTT thread: June 24, 2017, 02:41:40 AM "We've had some participants who purchased with USD of course. You simply fill out the form in cabinet when clicking on $ sign, fill out the form and get invoice sent to your email. After that you take it and go to the bank with it". Tokens never arrived . They claimed that I did not hit the buy button, but I transfered USD using the invoice provided. 8/16/17-"You did not press buy button:( You did not buy WTT. Please, send confirmation of payment to: fin@cryptonomos.com to refund." I did exactly this. I received no tokens and am unable to obtain a refund. Despite being promised a 24 hour refund, 5 DAYS ago and submitting copies of all records. 8/16/2017- "Refund will be done in 24 hours. You should press the buy button, sorry:("

Author: ICObox
Title: üåüüí∞[ANN] ICOBox (ICOS): Tokens of promising ICOs, at 75% off + Referral Program
Body: ICOS token: how does it work Nick Evdokimov Founder at ICOBox  Over the past few days, I‚Äôve received several hundred questions on the function of our ICOS token. To make things easy for everyone I decided to write this post which describes the principles of its operation and the market goals it accomplishes. The token holder‚Äôs task is to buy tokens during the time of shortage but as cheaply as possible. And now imagine that the token sale has been completed, the project started working and proved its worth, and you still have the opportunity to travel back in time and buy its tokens even cheaper than at its presale price. The project‚Äôs task is to conduct an impeccable ICO with an experienced team, and pay for the services with their own tokens. These are exactly the two tasks that are accomplished using the tool we at ICOBox invented. This tool is our ICOS token, which has the following characteristics: - Unprecedented discount. ICOS token can be swapped for any token issued with our tools at a 75% discount on the new token. This is possible because all funds collected through the ICOS token sale will be used to provide ICO services to new projects without any upfront payment on their part. In exchange, the ICOS platform and its token holders get a preset number of the project‚Äôs tokens: for example, if a startup received 50 BTC worth of services, it will repay to the platform 200 BTC worth of its tokens. So we get a ratio of 1:4, and, consequently, a 75% discount. So if you buy $1,000 worth of ICOS tokens, you could exchange them for tokens of other projects worth $4,000. - Minimization of risks. It is critically important that you can exchange your ICOS tokens at any time, whether at the start of the token sale or after its completion, and the timing of the exchange will have no affect on the exchange rate and the price. The tokens are available to you even when they are no longer available on the primary market. - High quality. We prescreen unacceptable ICO applications, and you select the best project by voting. It is really you who are selecting the projects which will be given the ICOBox‚Äôs tools. ICOS token is the first product token to be implemented using Ethereum (ERC-20) standard. Its function is similar to a discount card: It‚Äôs a tool which allows you to minimize both the cost of buying tokens and the risks associated with it. You control the situation at both stages of the process: during the voting and during the exchange. ICOS token is a key to a private club for token holders who are willing to cooperate with us to transform the ICO market to make it stable and vast. By buying ICOS tokens, you are making a significant contribution to the implementation of hundreds of quality projects ‚Äî naturally, with a dash of self-interest. We will be happy to welcome you to our ICOS token holder community.  https://medium.com/@neotopus/icos-token-how-does-it-work-f2a600fff5da

Token creates an ecosystem which allows those who creates new content (i.e. generates modes, draws new outfits etc.) to earn rewards.  Happy ICO!
